# ===== USER DATA — NEVER COMMIT =====
# All private data lives in ~/.aso-studio/ (outside the repo).
# These leftover legacy paths are kept ignored for safety in case anyone
# still has data in the old in-repo locations.

# aso-keywords legacy paths
aso-keywords/config/apps.json
aso-keywords/config/keywords/*.json
!aso-keywords/config/keywords/*.example.json
!aso-keywords/config/keywords/README.md
aso-keywords/data/

# aso-screenshots
aso-screenshots/data/
aso-screenshots/pdf/
aso-screenshots/exports/
aso-screenshots/server/lib/presets/imported/

# aso-video — generated mp4/png/audio assets can balloon to 100s of MB per
# session; never commit. Curated starter pack lives in `aso-video/workflows/`
# and `aso-video/influencer/` and ARE tracked.
aso-video/output/
aso-video/uploads/
aso-video/.tmp/

# Vite cache
**/.vite/
**/.vite-temp/

# Databases
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# Migrated raw data
*.jsonl
